## Biomarker Sync Endpoints

**POST /biomarkers/sync**
Submits one or more biomarker readings. Payload (JSON):
```json
{
  "user_id": "usr_abc123",
  "readings": [
    {"biomarker": "amh", "value": 18.3, "unit": "pmol/L", "date": "2024-03-20", "lab": "LabCorp"}
  ]
}
```
Returns: 200 with sync_id on success; 422 if unit mismatch or invalid biomarker code. Supported biomarker codes: amh, fsh, lh, e2, progesterone, testosterone_total, testosterone_free, vitamin_d, ferritin, folate_rbc, homocysteine, coq10, tsh, ft4.
